msgstr "Find and Replace II"


#: ../../es/writer-buscar-reemplazar-2.rst:13
msgid ""
"En este ejercicio vamos a usar la herramienta \"Buscar y reemplazar\" para "
"modificar un texto y sus atributos con Writer."
msgstr ""
"In this exercise we are going to use the \"Find and Replace\" tool to modify"
" a text and its attributes with Writer."


